<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pennyworth" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pennyworth,</orth> as much as is bought for a penny, no great quantity, a trifle: <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 44</bibl>.* <bibl n="shak. lll 3.103" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.650" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint IV, 4, 650</bibl> (<emph>though the p. on his side be the worst,</emph> i. e. though he have the worst of the bargain). <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 25</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.180" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 180</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.222" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 222</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.5.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 5, 4</bibl> (<emph>--s,</emph> viz of sleep).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>